{
  "texts": [
    "Initially, the GNN does not retrieve helpful information due to its limitation to understand natural language, i.e., that <jurisdiction.bodies> usually \"make the -3 114,196 14,274 14,274 497.9 99.0 laws\".",
    "GNN-RAG+RA retrieves the right information, helping the LLM answer the question correctly.",
    "We experiment with two widely used KGQA benchmarks: WebQuestionsSP (We-bQSP) (Yih et al., 2015), Complex WebQuestions 1.1 (CWQ) (Talmor and Berant, 2018).",
    "We also experiment with MetaQA-3 (Zhang et al., 2018) dataset.",
    "We provide the dataset statistics Table 8."
  ]
}